data.title: Joei Revilleza
data.content:
The Gallery at the State Library of New South Wales 🖼️
.
Beautiful paintings of Australians from times past and their respective legacy. Beside these collections was an interactive zone where you can take your selfie and place it on their digital collection. They said that everyone is a part of #newselfwales 😊
.
They provided a blank canvas for the children to draw a portrait of their own. Reminds me of Charlotte Mason's picture study. ❤️
.
